<h1>Work In A Professional Medical Environment</h1><br>
<h2>Los Angeles Hospital $13.27 HR + Overtime Available</h2><br>
<br>
<font size="5">For consideration go to <a href="http://securitasishiring.com/apply" rel="nofollow"> SecuritasIsHiring.com/apply</a> to complete an online application</font><br>
<br>
<font size="5">JOB DESCRIPTION:<br>
<br>
Do you enjoy working in a fast paced environment where your contributions make a difference? If so, this position should be right up your alley!!!<br>
<br>
As a security officer, based in a hospital environment, your duties include being a First Responder to emergency situations at the assigned facility.<br>
<br>
Additionally, you can make periodic tours to secure areas, provide customer service, mitigate behavioral sudden occurrences, deter crimes, and check for irregularities and to inspect protection devices and fire control equipment.<br>
<br>
Preserves order and may enforce regulations pertaining to personnel, visitors, and premises. Assist with the functions of physical and personal security and safety measures of members, patients, staff, and visitors. <br>
<br>
Protects staff and property from theft or damage, or persons from hazards or interference, including the potential for violence in the workplace.<br>
<br>
This position is ideal for those who have a flexible schedule, are comfortable writing detailed reports and enjoy working with others. We look forward to your application!!<br>
<br>
For consideration go to <a href="http://securitasishiring.com/apply" rel="nofollow"> SecuritasIsHiring.com/apply</a> to complete an online application<br><br>
BENEFITS:<br>
<br>
Major Medical/ Dental Available<br>
401K with Company Matching Contributions<br>
Life Insurance<br>
Vision Care<br>
Sons and Daughters Scholarship Program<br>
Free Uniforms<br>
Direct Deposit<br>
Excellence in Service (coupon sweepstakes) $50-$5000 prizes<br>
<br>
RECOGNITION:<br>
<br>
Years of Service Awards<br>
Customer Service Awards<br>
Service Hero of the Month<br>
Service Hero of the Year<br>
Supervisor of the Month<br>
Supervisor of the Year<br>
National Service Hero of the Year for Performance<br>
National Service Hero of the Year for Heroism<br>
Awards of Merit<br>
<br>For consideration go to <a href="http://securitasishiring.com/apply" rel="nofollow"> SecuritasIsHiring.com/apply</a> to complete an online application<br>
</font><br>
<br>
<br>
EOE/M/F/VETS/DISABILITIES <br>
PPO #14827<br>
<br>
Key Words: Security Guard, Security Officer, Security, Protective Agent, Watchman, Night Watchman, Day Watchman, Surveillance, Security, Surveillance Officer, Loss Prevention, Theft Prevention, Customer Service Security Officer, Hotel Security Officer, Safety and Security Officer, Store Detective, Area Patrol, Patrol Officer, Customer Service, Unarmed Security Guard, Public Safety, Public Safety Officer, Safety Officer, Correctional Officer, Driver Guard, Gate Guard, Facilities Guard, Facilities Safety, Concierge    </section>

